  "content_markdown": "1\n\n###  Application and Definitions\n\n1.1\n\nThis Part applies to:\n\n(1) every _firm_ that is a _UK designated investment firm_ ; and\n\n(2) a _CRR consolidation entity_.\n\n*Effective: 17/09/2021*\n\n1.2\n\nIn this Part, the following definitions shall apply:\n\n_COREP Regulation_\n\nmeans the Commission Implementing Regulation (EU) No 680/2014 of 16 April 2014 laying down implementing technical standards with regard to supervisory reporting of institutions according to Regulation (EU) No 575/2013 of the European Parliament and the Council, as amended from time to time.\n\n_Delegated Regulation_\n\nmeans Commission Delegated Regulation (EU) 2015/61 of 10 October 2014 to supplement Regulation (EU) No 575/2013 of the European Parliament and the Council with regard to liquidity coverage requirement for Credit Institutions, as amended from time to time.\n\n*Effective: 01/10/2015*\n\n1.3\n\nUnless otherwise defined, any italicised expression used in this Part and in the _CRR_ has the same meaning as in the _CRR_.\n\n*Effective: 01/10/2015*\n\n2\n\n###  Liquidity Coverage Requirement\n\n2.1\n\n  1. (1) For the purpose of complying with Article 412 (1) of the _CRR_, a _firm_ must comply with the obligations set out in the _Delegated Regulation_ as they apply to a _credit institution_ supervised pursuant to the _CRD_ , subject to the modifications in (2).\n  2. (2) For the purposes of (1):\n     1. (a) the provisions in Article 2(3) of the _Delegated Regulation_ do not apply where Article 12 of the ___CRR_ applies;\n     2. (b) the provisions in Article 2(3)(d) and Article 38 of the _Delegated Regulation_ do not apply; and\n     3. (c) any reference to _competent authority_ means a reference to the _PRA_.\n\n*Effective: 31/12/2020*\n\n3\n\n###  Compliance with Liquidity Reporting\n\n3.1\n\n[Deleted.]\n\n*Effective: 01/09/2022*\n\n3.2\n\n  1. (1) A _firm_ must comply with the reporting requirements laid down in Chapter 1 and Chapter 7 to Chapter 9 of the _COREP Regulation_ with the exception of Article 15 as they apply to a _credit institution_ supervised pursuant to the _CRD_.\n  2. (2) For the purpose of (1), a reference to Article 415 of the _CRR_ in the _COREP Regulation_ is construed as a reference to the obligations set out in (1).\n\n*Effective: 31/12/2020*\n\n4\n\n###  Application of this Part on an Individual Basis and a Consolidated Basis\n\n4.1\n\nThis Part applies to a _firm_ on an individual basis whether or not it also applies to the _firm_ on a _consolidated basis_.\n\n*Effective: 01/10/2015*\n  * [ Future  version of 4.1 after 01/01/2027  ](/pra-rules/liquidity-coverage-requirement---uk-designated-investment-firms/01-01-2027#fb8f2bda8e8f4e47b7e5368d817a3a3a)\n\n4.1A\n\nIf this Part applies to a _firm_ on an individual basis, the _firm_ must comply with the rules in this Part to the same extent and in the same manner as it is required to comply with the _firm’s_ obligations laid down in Part Six of the _CRR_.\n\n*Effective: 30/03/2018*\n  * [ Future  version of 4.1A after 01/01/2027  ](/pra-rules/liquidity-coverage-requirement---uk-designated-investment-firms/01-01-2027#21d0361f06ef48ad8306a63275874811)\n\n4.2\n\nA _CRR consolidation entity_ must comply with this Part on the basis of its _consolidated situation_.\n\n*Effective: 17/09/2021*\n  * [ Future  version of 4.2 after 01/01/2027  ](/pra-rules/liquidity-coverage-requirement---uk-designated-investment-firms/01-01-2027#28c90025da02441686d6fc2362dca970)\n\n4.3\n\n[deleted]\n\n*Effective: 17/09/2021*\n\n4.4\n\nIf this Part applies to a _firm_ or a _CRR consolidation entity_ on a _consolidated basis _or on a _sub-consolidated basis_ , it must carry out consolidation to the same extent and in the same manner as it is required to comply with the obligations laid down in Part Six of the _CRR _on a _consolidated basis _or _sub-consolidated basis_.\n\n*Effective: 17/09/2021*\n  * [ Future  version of 4.4 after 01/01/2027  ](/pra-rules/liquidity-coverage-requirement---uk-designated-investment-firms/01-01-2027#9590af00078d40d6be03f8c8a24b943e)\n\n5\n\n###  Transitional Provisions\n\n5.1\n\n[Deleted.]\n\n*Effective: 31/12/2020*",
  "content_html": "<div class=\"col9\">\n<div class=\"clear\"></div>\n\n\n<div class=\"part-content\">\n\n<div class=\"chapter-section\" data-version=\"6fce1e5051da475b8b98c5380f9bec15\" id=\"5dad11e011544fa3ab213de0ceb89a35\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number rule-number--mega chapter-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t1\r\n\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<h3 class=\"header-sans chapter-heading\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\tApplication and Definitions\r\n\t\t\t\t</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"29785bc59a4844b5b76a05a2e3a42b06\" id=\"b8194e0a77d44eb6b0af1a576289b570\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"1\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t1.1\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>This Part applies to:</p>\n<p>(1) every <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em> that is a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52120\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-aaa83e7b2694403288bada7cb4ccb9e1\" title=\"UK designated investment firm\">UK designated investment firm</a></em>; and </p>\n<p>(2) a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"128409\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-9abc7072e33941cca650790aec3d4ad6\" title=\"CRR consolidation entity\">CRR consolidation entity</a></em>.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t17/09/2021\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\n<a class=\"list-links__link icon-previous\" href=\"/pra-rules/liquidity-coverage-requirement---uk-designated-investment-firms/01-10-2015#b8194e0a77d44eb6b0af1a576289b570\">\r\n\t\t\tPast\r\n\t\t\t<span class=\"visually-hidden\">\r\n\t\t\t\tversion of 1.1 before 17/09/2021\r\n\t\t\t</span>\n</a>\n</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"79434267e1ba483fb5f0eeb575576148\" id=\"d40666b624ac4519a2f9be29f72b8a43\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t1.2\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>In this Part, the following definitions shall apply:</p>\n<p><em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"66784\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-3de89999f457451f926725d09b06fc5f\" title=\"COREP Regulation\">COREP Regulation</a></em></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">means the Commission Implementing Regulation (EU) No 680/2014 of 16 April 2014 laying down implementing technical standards with regard to supervisory reporting of institutions according to Regulation (EU) No 575/2013 of the European Parliament and the Council, as amended from time to time.</p>\n<p><em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"66785\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-84d6006763fe4ca1946f90e54301a0e3\" title=\"Delegated Regulation\">Delegated Regulation</a></em></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">means Commission Delegated Regulation (EU) 2015/61 of 10 October 2014 to supplement Regulation (EU) No 575/2013 of the European Parliament and the Council with regard to liquidity coverage requirement for Credit Institutions, as amended from time to time.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t01/10/2015\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"c49bb539fc0348e680d7d15637901bfe\" id=\"5622af5d8ff14d4f937e8dc45cec45c2\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t1.3\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>Unless otherwise defined, any italicised expression used in this Part and in the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52111\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-cbe45e8f942b45a4a7fe0d3550a6f2f3\" title=\"CRR\">CRR</a></em> has the same meaning as in the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52111\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-cbe45e8f942b45a4a7fe0d3550a6f2f3\" title=\"CRR\">CRR</a></em>.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t01/10/2015\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"page-utilities page-utilities--bg-grey\">\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"chapter-section\" data-version=\"eb2a83a785d34172b6e6ac2fa27c9e86\" id=\"10691fdb77094276923ebebf411baad5\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number rule-number--mega chapter-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t2\r\n\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<h3 class=\"header-sans chapter-heading\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\tLiquidity Coverage Requirement\r\n\t\t\t\t</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"b62e4450231b4f41b44fff8e59ee52af\" id=\"3ee1db32cf8b45d9807d05dbaef33bea\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t2.1\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<ol class=\"new-bullet\">\n<li>(1) For the purpose of complying with Article 412 (1) of the<em> <a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52111\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-cbe45e8f942b45a4a7fe0d3550a6f2f3\" title=\"CRR\">CRR</a></em>, a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em> must comply with the obligations set out in the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"66785\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-84d6006763fe4ca1946f90e54301a0e3\" title=\"Delegated Regulation\">Delegated Regulation</a></em> as they apply to a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52156\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-e2b606bf33474ecc99511b2096a6c145\" title=\"credit institution\">credit institution</a></em> supervised pursuant to the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52109\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-31e4b635ac0e45079e29954e3d518bec\" title=\"CRD\">CRD</a></em>, subject to the modifications in (2).</li>\n<li>(2) For the purposes of (1):</li>\n<ol>\n<li>(a) the provisions in Article 2(3) of the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"66785\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-84d6006763fe4ca1946f90e54301a0e3\" title=\"Delegated Regulation\">Delegated Regulation</a></em> do not apply where Article 12 of the<em> </em><em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52111\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-cbe45e8f942b45a4a7fe0d3550a6f2f3\" title=\"CRR\">CRR</a></em> applies;</li>\n<li>(b) the provisions in Article 2(3)(d) and Article 38 of the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"66785\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-84d6006763fe4ca1946f90e54301a0e3\" title=\"Delegated Regulation\">Delegated Regulation</a></em> do not apply; and</li>\n<li>(c) any reference to <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"66786\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-5ead196cb73c43b08eaf33907d36d757\" title=\"competent authority\">competent authority</a></em> means a reference to the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52117\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-494fbb81077e408f84519b8c66998fef\" title=\"PRA\">PRA</a></em>.</li>\n</ol>\n</ol>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t31/12/2020\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\n<a class=\"list-links__link icon-previous\" href=\"/pra-rules/liquidity-coverage-requirement---uk-designated-investment-firms/01-10-2015#3ee1db32cf8b45d9807d05dbaef33bea\">\r\n\t\t\tPast\r\n\t\t\t<span class=\"visually-hidden\">\r\n\t\t\t\tversion of 2.1 before 31/12/2020\r\n\t\t\t</span>\n</a>\n</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"page-utilities page-utilities--bg-grey\">\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"chapter-section\" data-version=\"0940049181e044dbb4c117de346f8e1c\" id=\"9a9e988e67df458088a2bb9ef28cde82\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number rule-number--mega chapter-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t3\r\n\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<h3 class=\"header-sans chapter-heading\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\tCompliance with Liquidity Reporting\r\n\t\t\t\t</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"cec06ab4bd43445298d67052ab613d99\" id=\"f975106f7d8b4119859f1f020f64efe8\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t3.1\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>[Deleted.]</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t01/09/2022\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\n<a class=\"list-links__link icon-previous\" href=\"/pra-rules/liquidity-coverage-requirement---uk-designated-investment-firms/01-10-2015#f975106f7d8b4119859f1f020f64efe8\">\r\n\t\t\tPast\r\n\t\t\t<span class=\"visually-hidden\">\r\n\t\t\t\tversion of 3.1 before 01/09/2022\r\n\t\t\t</span>\n</a>\n</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"194ab644f020456d9050ab416d4c6451\" id=\"f542523e2c744047aac7e4959d160141\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t3.2\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<ol class=\"new-bullet\">\n<li>(1) A <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em> must comply with the reporting requirements laid down in Chapter 1 and Chapter 7 to Chapter 9 of the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"66784\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-3de89999f457451f926725d09b06fc5f\" title=\"COREP Regulation\">COREP Regulation</a></em> with the exception of Article 15 as they apply to a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52156\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-e2b606bf33474ecc99511b2096a6c145\" title=\"credit institution\">credit institution</a></em> supervised pursuant to the<em> <a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52109\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-31e4b635ac0e45079e29954e3d518bec\" title=\"CRD\">CRD</a></em>.</li>\n<li>(2) For the purpose of (1), a reference to Article 415 of the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52111\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-cbe45e8f942b45a4a7fe0d3550a6f2f3\" title=\"CRR\">CRR</a></em> in the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"66784\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-3de89999f457451f926725d09b06fc5f\" title=\"COREP Regulation\">COREP Regulation</a></em> is construed as a reference to the obligations set out in (1).</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t31/12/2020\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\n<a class=\"list-links__link icon-previous\" href=\"/pra-rules/liquidity-coverage-requirement---uk-designated-investment-firms/01-10-2015#f542523e2c744047aac7e4959d160141\">\r\n\t\t\tPast\r\n\t\t\t<span class=\"visually-hidden\">\r\n\t\t\t\tversion of 3.2 before 31/12/2020\r\n\t\t\t</span>\n</a>\n</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"page-utilities page-utilities--bg-grey\">\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"chapter-section\" data-version=\"2e2802653b8b4e9c82dbe04a6e58a24a\" id=\"d67d0c56cbac474d81607c94a1b2d63a\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number rule-number--mega chapter-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t4\r\n\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<h3 class=\"header-sans chapter-heading\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\tApplication of this Part on an Individual Basis and a Consolidated Basis\r\n\t\t\t\t</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"377670212e0c4d589bc9cb5230a60b95\" id=\"fb8f2bda8e8f4e47b7e5368d817a3a3a\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"1\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t4.1\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>This Part applies to a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em> on an individual basis whether or not it also applies to the<em> <a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em> on a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"66787\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-9ef4c0e03dd24bb39cf96cfddff4de4f\" title=\"consolidated basis\">consolidated basis</a></em>.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t01/10/2015\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n<li class=\"list-links__item list-future\">\n<a class=\"list-links__link icon-future\" href=\"/pra-rules/liquidity-coverage-requirement---uk-designated-investment-firms/01-01-2027#fb8f2bda8e8f4e47b7e5368d817a3a3a\">\r\n\t\t\tFuture\r\n\t\t\t<span class=\"visually-hidden\">\r\n\t\t\t\tversion of 4.1 after 01/01/2027\r\n\t\t\t</span>\n</a>\n</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"ecf28500fdd240c29c719494231e5372\" id=\"21d0361f06ef48ad8306a63275874811\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t4.1A\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>If this Part applies to a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em> on an individual basis, the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em> must comply with the rules in this Part to the same extent and in the same manner as it is required to comply with the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm’s</a></em> obligations laid down in Part Six of the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52111\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-cbe45e8f942b45a4a7fe0d3550a6f2f3\" title=\"CRR\">CRR</a></em>.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t30/03/2018\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n<li class=\"list-links__item list-future\">\n<a class=\"list-links__link icon-future\" href=\"/pra-rules/liquidity-coverage-requirement---uk-designated-investment-firms/01-01-2027#21d0361f06ef48ad8306a63275874811\">\r\n\t\t\tFuture\r\n\t\t\t<span class=\"visually-hidden\">\r\n\t\t\t\tversion of 4.1A after 01/01/2027\r\n\t\t\t</span>\n</a>\n</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"de8432227b404ee78e81bdcfa8dbd739\" id=\"28c90025da02441686d6fc2362dca970\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t4.2\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>A <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"128409\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-9abc7072e33941cca650790aec3d4ad6\" title=\"CRR consolidation entity\">CRR consolidation entity</a></em> must comply with this Part on the basis of its <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"66788\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-21df64bea795412ebb72351a8ae028b6\" title=\"consolidated situation\">consolidated situation</a></em>.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t17/09/2021\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\n<a class=\"list-links__link icon-previous\" href=\"/pra-rules/liquidity-coverage-requirement---uk-designated-investment-firms/31-12-2020#28c90025da02441686d6fc2362dca970\">\r\n\t\t\tPast\r\n\t\t\t<span class=\"visually-hidden\">\r\n\t\t\t\tversion of 4.2 before 17/09/2021\r\n\t\t\t</span>\n</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"list-links__item list-future\">\n<a class=\"list-links__link icon-future\" href=\"/pra-rules/liquidity-coverage-requirement---uk-designated-investment-firms/01-01-2027#28c90025da02441686d6fc2362dca970\">\r\n\t\t\tFuture\r\n\t\t\t<span class=\"visually-hidden\">\r\n\t\t\t\tversion of 4.2 after 01/01/2027\r\n\t\t\t</span>\n</a>\n</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"25b1c8b66229402a9cfd8ded59667a4c\" id=\"f5bd9df89bcd4581a1272daa8da8a382\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t4.3\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>[deleted]</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t17/09/2021\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\n<a class=\"list-links__link icon-previous\" href=\"/pra-rules/liquidity-coverage-requirement---uk-designated-investment-firms/31-12-2020#f5bd9df89bcd4581a1272daa8da8a382\">\r\n\t\t\tPast\r\n\t\t\t<span class=\"visually-hidden\">\r\n\t\t\t\tversion of 4.3 before 17/09/2021\r\n\t\t\t</span>\n</a>\n</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"dba53a92b94a4500820eb598bcb7e35b\" id=\"9590af00078d40d6be03f8c8a24b943e\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t4.4\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>If this Part applies to a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em> or a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"128409\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-9abc7072e33941cca650790aec3d4ad6\" title=\"CRR consolidation entity\">CRR consolidation entity</a></em> on a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"66787\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-9ef4c0e03dd24bb39cf96cfddff4de4f\" title=\"consolidated basis\">consolidated basis</a> </em>or on a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"78070\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-258d366b40e64d2385ad3d800d1f9400\" title=\"sub-consolidated basis\">sub-consolidated basis</a></em>, it must carry out consolidation to the same extent and in the same manner as it is required to comply with the obligations laid down in Part Six of the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52111\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-cbe45e8f942b45a4a7fe0d3550a6f2f3\" title=\"CRR\">CRR</a> </em>on a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"66787\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-9ef4c0e03dd24bb39cf96cfddff4de4f\" title=\"consolidated basis\">consolidated basis</a> </em>or <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"78070\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-258d366b40e64d2385ad3d800d1f9400\" title=\"sub-consolidated basis\">sub-consolidated basis</a></em>.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t17/09/2021\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\n<a class=\"list-links__link icon-previous\" href=\"/pra-rules/liquidity-coverage-requirement---uk-designated-investment-firms/30-03-2018#9590af00078d40d6be03f8c8a24b943e\">\r\n\t\t\tPast\r\n\t\t\t<span class=\"visually-hidden\">\r\n\t\t\t\tversion of 4.4 before 17/09/2021\r\n\t\t\t</span>\n</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"list-links__item list-future\">\n<a class=\"list-links__link icon-future\" href=\"/pra-rules/liquidity-coverage-requirement---uk-designated-investment-firms/01-01-2027#9590af00078d40d6be03f8c8a24b943e\">\r\n\t\t\tFuture\r\n\t\t\t<span class=\"visually-hidden\">\r\n\t\t\t\tversion of 4.4 after 01/01/2027\r\n\t\t\t</span>\n</a>\n</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"page-utilities page-utilities--bg-grey\">\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"chapter-section\" data-version=\"a8abbcb948b24c7eb0cbb289e0b17169\" id=\"a7dd463099d5486489dd089cff5628b0\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number rule-number--mega chapter-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t5\r\n\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<h3 class=\"header-sans chapter-heading\">\r\n\